"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"To be a business, every action should be marketing in essence and should serve to make money. Eliminate waste of energy and reduce wasteful actions. When working in the company, think of you to do this\\n\\nIs this thing conducive to the company's marketing activities, is it to make money for the company? For example, Huawei's Ren Zhengfei, people from JPMorgan Chase came to Ren Zhengfei, and Ren Zhengfei did not see him, people from JPMorgan Chase said, \\\"Ren Zhengfei, you are too arrogant, you have rejected the richest group in the world.\\\" And Ren Zhengfei said: If you are here to buy products from me, even if you are a small self-employed, I will treat you respectfully, but you are here to talk about your business, and this has nothing to do with me. Some companies require waste paper to be reused, which seems to be very economical. In fact, this is a trivial matter. It is the boss that really should be calculated. Is the management's energy used in the company's profitable business? Is the way of doing things optimized? Point should learn from Ren Zhengfei.\\n\\nAs an entrepreneurial boss, I see that many people go everywhere to participate in the entrepreneurial circle, to form friendships with others, instead of researching their own companyâ€™s business. This is also a waste of energy. Of course, in a deeper level, there are many employees who are leaving the company. Communication is a waste of energy, just let people do it. Every action of the boss must be for marketing and for the company\\n\\nEntrepreneur Business School Serving Entrepreneurs 151\\n\\nThe overall profitability of the service. As long as the boss follows my line of thinking, your business performance should be immediate\\n\\nThere will be a substantial improvement.\\n\\nAnother core mission of the company is to train partners. The biggest task of partners is to train new partners. Only those who become shareholders will work hard for the company; the biggest task of middle-level employees is to train their own successors; to train them as their own responsibility, and to train them at any cost. them!\\n\\nAttracting talent is a by-product of cultivating talent internally. Because people can be nurtured and promoted here, everyone else is willing to come, instead of going outside to dig out tall people. The company can make a lot of money because it has a lot of talents.\",\"timestamp\":1634797891,\"title\":\"Marketing is the essence of everything\"},\"digest\":\"Toecz1EhhTnF8G7Une4gUs3LYISRpyDP3rSInWUWnUE\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x0500e3b6f7b1214a11851b9B348020C08018403b\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"nKf8ZamRyX8cLVb8DeIErgOMrQgMun7f02Hq_yDPgjE\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"3htkpr16jLLCk2n5vgcjMXkGx9Ypl9sCU0ngm5GUXu8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"i4yO9F9HXfeZM6W5RIyml_X-68vybe_1kMl4hY9Bidt5W7Xy-h7rznhQimdmFlldki4t96HPBfHlgXgA9yjY6Q\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x1c6f856baad7dbcdc04a289cfb8c27fd2d4c254469eae7a6d5e283ce19250e091ab85676074d27b49e23c7d4b78b5f81e8536a0da448b30920c0f4dc5a6602e41c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"nKf8ZamRyX8cLVb8DeIErgOMrQgMun7f02Hq_yDPgjE\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"3htkpr16jLLCk2n5vgcjMXkGx9Ypl9sCU0ngm5GUXu8\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"Toecz1EhhTnF8G7Une4gUs3LYISRpyDP3rSInWUWnUE\"}"